The paper deals with face recognition using deep CNNs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves multi-task learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of dynamic updates to the weights of tasks, which is a common approach in optimization and meta-learning (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques such as deep learning and neural networks (cs.AI, cs.NE).
